# Default Marco 1 prelude: a 4-manifold with its tangent bundle, and the
# three tensor heads exercised by the acceptance tests -- Riemann, the
# metric, and the rank-3 Levi-Civita symbol.

manifold M dim 4
bundle TM on M dim 4

head R : TM*, TM*, TM*, TM* symmetry (1 2)- (3 4)- (1 3)(2 4)+
head g : TM*, TM* symmetry (1 2)+
head eps : TM*, TM*, TM* symmetry antisymmetric
